Class PointOfInterest

java.lang.Object
trails.PointOfInterest
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<PointOfInterest>
public class PointOfInterest
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<PointOfInterest>
This class represents any waypoints (points of interest) that can be found on a particular trail.
